				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12268224#post-4364090</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12268224/scp-4790#post-4364090</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 15 Sep 2019 03:07:30 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Lt Flops</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1735419</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>Are the Priorihominus also intended to be the creators of SCP-1795?</p> </blockquote> <p>It wasn't my intention, but I <em>was</em> aware of SCP-1795 when putting together some of the ideas here. I will say that the two have undeniable thematic similarities and both involve an advanced early human presence.</p> <p>To add to this, even a basic analysis of the <em>Priorihominus</em> civilization points to them having a wide interstellar reach, with sufficiently advanced (para-)technology.<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-622990-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" >1</a></sup> Large-scale planetary manufacturing might look a bit outside their capabilities &#8212; but we also don't have a timescale! If these are generation ships, then it's likely they were launched in the infancy of their extrasolar civilization.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;and&nbsp;spoiler&nbsp;territory</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>Couple things:</p> <ul> <li>The &quot;Minotaur&quot; is pattern screamers, which can be linked to their appearance in 1795. Additionally, the debris field is similar to what <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3426">post-3426</a> would look like (albeit on the extreme end of the spectrum).</li> <li>Something that came before us <em>did</em> have the capacity to create <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-002-ex">megastructures</a> beyond the planetary scale.</li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> <p>So, if you do want to headcanon a connection, I definitely won't protest it!</p> <div class="footnotes-footer"> <div class="title">Footnotes</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-622990-1"><a href="javascript:;" >1</a>. They had the industrial and engineering capacity to manufacture a fleet of Klein bottle generation ships, and were familiar with this &quot;Minotaur&quot; when they found it.</div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
