					<![CDATA[
						 <p>As already mentioned, the atmosphere here is really great and outright chilling. Definitely a good read.</p> <p>Also, considering the implications here, are the Priorihominus also intended to be the creators of <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-1795">SCP-1795</a>?</p> 
				 	]]>
