					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Thanks, Crashington! I went through a lot of different iterations while drafting this, and <em>really</em> tried to take into account each and every critter's thoughts before proceeding to the next. There was a ton of deliberation when figuring out how much information should be relayed to the reader, what should be omitted, and which tidbits contribute positively to the central premise. I don't expect every reader to understand everything going on &#8212; but I <em>am</em> happy with the final product!</p> 
				 	]]>
