					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12268224#post-4320074</guid>
				<title>An easy +1</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12268224/scp-4790#post-4320074</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2019 03:35:36 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>ManyMeats</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2104082</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This has improved quite a bit since your draft; you've put the crit of all involved to very good use.</p> <p>This piece just really very easily encapsulates <em>atmosphere</em>. I feel unsettled almost the entire time I am reading this once we get going and it doesn't let up. I'm not 100% sure I have even uncovered all the mysteries hinted at in this article but I think that just makes it all the better. The tone here is simply <strong>mastered</strong> for the type of story you're trying to tell.</p> <p>Very easy +1, great job.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
