					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12268224#post-4319939</guid>
				<title>SCP-4790: Do not go gentle into that good night.</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12268224/scp-4790#post-4319939</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2019 23:04:34 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Lt Flops</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1735419</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <div style="text-align: center;"> <blockquote> <p><strong><a href="https://youtu.be/gSkIwwdT79E" target="_blank">Do not go gentle into that good night,</a></strong><br /> <strong><a href="https://youtu.be/gSkIwwdT79E" target="_blank">Old age should burn and rave at close of day;</a></strong><br /> <strong><a href="https://youtu.be/gSkIwwdT79E" target="_blank">Rage, rage against the dying of the light.</a></strong><br /></p> <div style="text-align: right;"> <p><strong>&#8212;Dylan Thomas</strong></p> </div> </blockquote> </div> <blockquote> <p><strong>SCP-4790:</strong> Do not go gentle into that good night.<br /> <strong>Author:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580938590" alt="Lt Flops" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" >Lt Flops</a></span></p> </blockquote> <hr /> <p>This article is set in the <strong><a target="_blank" href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/ad-astra-per-aspera-hub">Ad Astra Per Aspera</a></strong> Canon. I've wanted to write a cosmic horror-inspired article for a while now, and I hoped to get this out there as soon as I could.</p> <hr /> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▷&nbsp;Special&nbsp;Thanks&nbsp;and&nbsp;Image&nbsp;Attribution</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:110%;"><strong>Special Thanks &#8212; Critters &amp; Beta Readers</strong></span></p> <p><strong>▷</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crashington" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5028224&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580938590" alt="Crashington" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5028224)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crashington" >Crashington</a></span><br /> <strong>▷</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nameless-mediocre" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4176498&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580938590" alt="Nameless Mediocre" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4176498)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nameless-mediocre" >Nameless Mediocre</a></span><br /> <strong>▷</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/westrin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2858989&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580938590" alt="Westrin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2858989)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/westrin" >Westrin</a></span><br /> <strong>▷</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2727655&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580938590" alt="Weryllium" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2727655)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" >Weryllium</a></span><br /> <strong>▷</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yossipossi" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2199269&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580938590" alt="Yossipossi" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2199269)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yossipossi" >Yossipossi</a></span><br /> <strong>▷</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nerdibbles" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2822872&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580938590" alt="Nerdibbles" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2822872)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nerdibbles" >Nerdibbles</a></span><br /> <strong>▷</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/natvoltaic" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2800867&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580938590" alt="NatVoltaic" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2800867)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/natvoltaic" >NatVoltaic</a></span><br /> <strong>▷</strong> KindlyTurtleClem<br /> <strong>▷</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cerastes" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3352053&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580938590" alt="Cerastes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3352053)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cerastes" >Cerastes</a></span><br /> <strong>▷</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/manymeats" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2104082&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580938590" alt="ManyMeats" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2104082)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/manymeats" >ManyMeats</a></span><br /> <strong>▷</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/alandaris" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3146689&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580938590" alt="AlanDaris" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3146689)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/alandaris" >AlanDaris</a></span></p> <hr /> <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:110%;"><strong>Image Attribution</strong></span></p> <p><strong>▷ <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/hubble_esa/29230946621/" target="_blank">Alpha Centauri</a> – CC BY 2.0</strong><br /> <strong>▷ <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/component:the-way-out-theme#toc1" target="_blank">Overwatch Command logo</a> – CC BY-SA 3.0</strong></p> <hr /> <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:110%;"><strong>Research Data</strong></span></p> <p><strong>▷ <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alpha_Centauri" target="_blank">Alpha Centauri article</a></strong></p> </div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">△&nbsp;Close</a></div> </div> </div> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▷&nbsp;Background&nbsp;Info/Spoilers</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <hr /> <ul> <li><strong><em>Priorihominus</em>:</strong> A previous iteration of humanity. Whether they were destroyed outright or went into hiding is unclear.</li> <li><strong><em>Chekov-.009</em>: <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chekhov%27s_gun" target="_blank">Chekhov's gun</a></strong>. Left in the system, unfired and alone.</li> <li><strong>Lang Distortion Drive:</strong> A para-technological engine allowing for faster-than-light travel via spacetime manipulations. Essentially, hacking reality to make your ship go faster. It's mentioned in <strong><a target="_blank" href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-3230">other</a> <a target="_blank" href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-4774">Ad Astra</a> <a target="_blank" href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/faster-than-light-prelude">articles</a></strong>. In-universe, they're experimental and very prone to malfunction, but they get the job done. In any case, it's why the ship gets to Alpha Centauri so quickly (in 160 days &#8212; faster-than-light by an order of magnitude).</li> </ul> </div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">△&nbsp;Close</a></div> </div> </div> <hr /> <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:130%;"><strong><a target="_blank" href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/floppyphoenix">If you liked this, check out my Author Page!</a></strong></span></p> 
				 	]]>
